{
  "stem": "14463.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I will never forget it, that evening, because again, I went to the river.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this time I didn't steal, but I was catching some fish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I brought it to Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Wulkan.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Wulkan made fish, something out of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, she made something out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was-- you know, there was-- for some reason, they had a small hut.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was only a few families in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was a stove in the middle in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she was cooking in there, that-- the fish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were saying the Haggadah, [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was explaining to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was a great man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, he was-- yeah, he was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then now come time for, to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she took the fish and put it on the table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "On the way, she fell, and the fish fell down the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "At that time, I made myself a mental note.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I promised myself that from now on, wherever I'll be, if I'll live through this thing, that Pesach will be strict, in my home, wherever I live.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Till today, Pesach in our home is like in a rabbi's place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Everything is locked, and everything is shut, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Everything is [INAUDIBLE] and everything is so kosher that you've got no idea.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I love it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was from that moment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "This is what I remember from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I also remember when the war finished-- when the war started, between the Russia and Poland-- and Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now this is a most interesting story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't think that anybody has got anything like it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know of anyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I told you, I was very perceptive.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
